<h1>Hifz.World</h1>
<p class="meta">Memorize and review the Qur’an with Mushaf reading, qirāʾāt comparison, and live feedback from a listener.</p>

<p>
  Hifz.World is an iOS app for huffāz and students: read a clear Mushaf, save page bundles for review,
  share them with a teacher or friend, and get marks while you recite.
</p>

